Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說……密羅奇尼亞行星也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是被我們毀滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的也是魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我順便告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實魔石索沙是將行星上的生命能量吸收之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再將它傳送到異次元空間的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要做這種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是靠這種方式賴以維生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其他星球的生命能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都將成為我們活動所需的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去如此，今後也是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做卡布力爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是魔石索沙的魂魄……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為了自己的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不惜毀滅別的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種行為根本就是天理不容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!你這句話倒挺像是救世主會說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來到現在你們還不知道你們自己扮演了什麼角色?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你們當作是餞別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是尼德行星的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別派遣到這個星球的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是要找尋這個與我交手的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜是個巫女?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上她也算達成這份艱難的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她繼承了巫女的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過漫長的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算走到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中唯一的錯誤就是你…克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不是什麼救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你實在是太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上會讓你知道……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的無能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本就沒有任何力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這種程度已經很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是快點放下肩上的這個重擔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職司電光明滅的雷界王-塞基拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自血脈中釋放熾烈難當的雷火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴雷擊(ThunderBolt)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你們接近克勞德和蕾娜一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕舉妄動絕對會被打成蜂窩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣要怎麼去救克勞德啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，克勞德還有蕾娜不知道會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們只有看的份?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們去了也不一定能夠幫的上什麼忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣實在太不甘心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖潔的光輝……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『將這道聖潔的光輝導向正軌…』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『就能將惡魔毀滅於無形』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩，你有什麼發現嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本古書上寫的聖潔的光輝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是指『拉克爾赫普』嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…聖潔的光輝另有所指?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德跟我說過不到最後不要放棄希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要抱持著一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的聖潔之光……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧?克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要搞清楚，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就沒有資格做救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不是我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卡布力爾製造出來的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你心裡複製出來的這個我卻比任何人都還要瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過是個無名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，情勢已經不是你可以掌控的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個行星再過不久就會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是無可逃避的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你根本就不是艾斯貝爾的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有義務跟這裡的人一起送命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義、友情、愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想為這些冠晃堂皇的虛名捨棄生命嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用捨棄生命也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點停止吧!克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你的價值與樹根還有石頭沒什麼差別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不能怪罪到你的身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來就沒有認為自己是救世主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我自己比誰都還要清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也就是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才比任何人都瞭解大家的痛苦和悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我想要保護他們的心也比任何人都要強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鳳破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你已經成長到這個地步了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…你還沒有能打倒我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要說拯救這個星球了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會搖得這麼厲害啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西絲，危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅卻(Extinction)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩，你好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的真面目嗎?卡布力爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是負責執行卡布力爾大人意志的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是『魔石索沙』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這趟漫長的旅程就到今天為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…保護你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒是……?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此請與這聖潔之光一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主啊…聖潔的戰士啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此借巫女的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秉持聖石之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予你光之劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你能以此拯救所有的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡布力爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你一個人能做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能夠保護得了誰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電十字(ThunderCross)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在!克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多跟我有著同樣信念的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去一直躲在爸爸背影後面的那個我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了這些同伴們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…爸爸對我一直是不可逾越的高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都會拿我們父子比較
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看到的我只是個大英雄的獨生子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這個世界上遇到的同伴卻不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們的眼中我只是一個\N叫做克勞德·C·肯尼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了他們才讓我重新找回了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡這些同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想起他們的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得滿腔熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湧出源源不絕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我才體會到爸爸將雷射槍交給我的用心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我一直認為爸爸是為了無能的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把他自己的武器交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是我的誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望我能夠保護自己最寶貝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是爸爸當初將雷射槍交給我的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我終於瞭解到爸爸的用心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這雙手保護我最重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖潔的光輝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!那就是聖潔的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德，你絕對會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害，你好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥還結束呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是無法終止我的主人這項偉大的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡布力爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們既然把魔石索沙解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的月亮不就應該消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟這個星球一起滅亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐，是你停止了時間之流嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你魔族之王…也不可能全身而退的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命會耗盡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這場充滿勇氣的戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都看在眼裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到我來保護這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時作為承認你們的證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當我的生命耗盡之時\N時間將再次流動…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做我該做得事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也去完成該做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救艾斯貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不會再有第二第三個艾斯貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空傳送裝置…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該做的事…\N就是利用這個裝置去敵人的根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後切斷一切萬惡的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有辦法做到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打倒真正的敵人之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的旅程不會結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你不會一個人去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發
